cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.AI

The paper discusses the use of online scientific archives and analysis tools, which are primarily driven by computer programs. This suggests that the paper may belong to the categories of cs.DL (Digital Libraries), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper mentions the self-organization and cross-correlation of data from different archives, which could fall under the categories of cs.CY (Computational Geometry) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
